data: what are the medications of depression?

Many types of antidepressant medications are available to treat depression, including: 

Selective serotonin reuptake inhibitors (SSRIs), Serotonin and norepinephrine reuptake inhibitors 

(SNRIs), Atypical antidepressants, Tricyclic antidepressants, Monoamine oxidase inhibitors (MAOIs) 

as well as Other medications.
What are the symptoms of coronavirus?
People may experience; cough, fever, tiredness, difficulty breathing (severe cases).
what is the role of th17 cells?

Th17 cells, by virtue of their production of IL-17 and IL-17F, are generally thought to be pro-

inflammatory and play an important role in host defense against infection, by recruiting neutrophils 

and macrophages to infected tissues.
what is the role of rorc in ibd?

RORc is the main transcription factor controlling Th17 cells phenotype and hence this transcription 

factor regulates Th17 function during health and disease including IBD.
